erical shape\nhas only a very small effect on the barrier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2015 16:37:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 May 2015 10:57:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
